                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-248-18700228 t18700228-248-punishment-3"></join>Eighteen Months' Imprisonment.</rs>
                  </hi>—<hi rend="largeCaps">LOWE</hi> received a good character—Strongly recommended to mercy—<rs id="t18700228-248-punishment-4" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18700228-248-punishment-4" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18700228-248-punishment-4" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-248-18700228 t18700228-248-punishment-4"></join>Three Months' Imprisonment.</rs>
